text: The area of Tomamae District in Rumoi Subprefecture. is a district located in Rumoi Subprefecture, Hokkaido, Japan. As of 2004, the district has an estimated population of 14,828 and a density of 12.28 persons per km². The total area is 1,207.03 km². ==Towns and villages== *Haboro *Shosanbetsu *Tomamae Category:Districts in Hokkaido
